#
# User credentials helper
# for various user scripts and programs
#

Default database is stored in $HOME/.passwd
All credentials are in plain text.

This is not meant to be used to store actual
sensitive information. Just easy and unified
access for automated scripts and programs
that just happen to need credentials.

Supported languages:
   - Shell

To use this library, source/include the
/arch/passwd/libpasswd-<language>

And then refer to the include file for further
documentation.
